    <para id="id1165193776718">As a result of the industrial synthesis of ammonia Germany was able to manufacture sufficient explosives to fight until 11 November 1918, by which time almost 10 million were dead, almost 7 million missing, and over 21 million were wounded (<link target-id="id1165183372488"/>).</para>


